  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Join My Village (JMV) - Malawi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Personal and Professional capacity development: The project is building girls&apos; capacity and skills to gain more self confidence through assertiveness training, strengthening of girls peer mentoring, role modelling. In addition the project building capacity of  teachers&apos; continuous professional development. 					
Institutional strengthening and improving learning and teaching environment: The project is working with school governing boards, in particular SMCs and mother groups to promote enabling learning environment for girls and advocate for equitable deployment of teachers. The project is also working with the community to construct school infrastructure.					
Household Economic empowerment: This is mainly through supporting Village Savings and Loan in order to increase households to be able to meet minimum education needs for their children.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
